   Shaukat, Kamran, Univ Punjab, Dept Data Sci, Lahore 54590, Pakistan.
   Alam, Talha Mahboob, Virtual Univ Pakistan, Dept Comp Sci \& Informat Technol, Lahore 54000, Pakistan.
   Hameed, Ibrahim A., Norwegian Univ Sci \& Technol, Dept ICT \& Nat Sci, N-7491 Trondheim, Norway.
