   Nweke, Henry Friday, Ebonyi State Univ, Comp Sci Dept, PMB 053, Abakaliki, Ebonyi State, Nigeria.
   Mujtaba, Ghulam, Sukkur IBA Univ, Dept Comp Sci, Sukkur 65200, Pakistan.
