   Cai, Zhong-Kui, Nanjing Tech Univ, Coll Civil Engn, Nanjing 211816, Peoples R China.
   Chen, Guang-Ming; Zhao, Xin-Yu, South China Univ Technol, State Key Lab Subtrop Bldg Sci, Guangzhou 510641, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.engstruct.2023.117225},
