   Mondal, Sukanta, Birla Inst Technol \& Sci Pilani, Dept Biol Sci, KK Birla Goa Campus, Zuarinagar 403726, Goa, India.
   Joseph, Alex, Manipal Acad Higher Educ, Manipal Coll Pharmaceut Sci, Dept Pharmaceut Chem, Manipal 576104, Karnataka, India.},
DOI = {10.1002/minf.201900062},
