   Delplanque, Jean-Pierre, Univ Calif Davis, Dept Mech \& Aerosp Engn, Davis, CA 95616 USA.
   Anderson, Nicholas R., Univ Calif Davis, Dept Publ Hlth Sci, Sacramento, CA 95817 USA.
   Chuah, Chen-Nee, Univ Calif Davis, Dept Elect \& Comp Engn, Davis, CA 95616 USA.},
