   Jiang, Weili, Sichuan Univ, Coll Comp Sci, Chengdu, Peoples R China.
   Zhou, Kangneng, Univ Sci \& Technol Beijing, Sch Comp \& Commun Engn, Beijing, Peoples R China.
   Xiong, Chenchen, Natl Engn Res Ctr Beijing Biochip Technol, Beijing, Peoples R China.
   Du, Guodong, Xiamen Univ, Dept Artificial Intelligence, Xiamen, Peoples R China.
