Affiliation = {Sadegh-Zadeh, SA (Corresponding Author), Staffordshire Univ, Sch Digital Technol \& Arts, Dept Comp, Stoke On Trent ST4 2DE, England.
   Hajiyavand, AM (Corresponding Author), Univ Birmingham, Sch Engn, Dept Mech Engn, Birmingham B15 2SQ, England.
