Affiliation = {Ryu, KH (Corresponding Author), Ton Duc Thang Univ, Fac Informat Technol, Ho Chi Minh City 700000, Vietnam.
   Ryu, KH (Corresponding Author), Chungbuk Natl Univ, Dept Comp Sci, Coll Elect \& Comp Engn, Cheongju 28644, South Korea.
