   Van Calster, Ben, Katholieke Univ Leuven, Leuven Unit Hlth Technol Assessment Res LUHTAR, Leuven, Belgium.
   Rohmann, Jessica L., Charite Univ Med Berlin, Ctr Stroke Res Berlin, Berlin, Germany.
   Konigorski, Stefan, Hasso Plattner Inst Digital Hlth Mt Sinai, Icahn Sch Med Mt Sinai, New York, NY USA.
   van Smeden, Maarten, Univ Utrecht, UMC Utrecht, Julius Ctr Hlth Sci \& Primary Care, Utrecht, Netherlands.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.jbi.2024.104666},
EarlyAccessDate = {JUN 2024},
Article-Number = {104666},
Keywords = {Class imbalance; Prediction; Calibration; Discrimination; Undersampling},
