   Alkhammash, Eman H., Taif Univ, Coll Comp \& Informat Technol, Dept Comp Sci, At Taif 21944, Saudi Arabia.
   Hadjouni, Myriam, Princess Nourah Bint Abdulrahman Univ, Coll Comp \& Informat Sci, Dept Comp Sci, Riyadh 11671, Saudi Arabia.},
DOI = {10.1109/ACCESS.2022.3150047},
Keywords = {Feature extraction; Data models; Deep learning; Smart meters; Generative
