   human body constituents; hyper parameter tuning; KAPH; optimized
   training model; PITT; VATT},
Keywords-Plus = {NEURAL-NETWORK; OPTIMIZATION; RELIABILITY; ALGORITHM; MODEL},
Author-Email = {vishumadaan123@gmail.com},
Number-of-Cited-References = {40},
