Affiliation = {Cao, P (Corresponding Author), Northeastern Univ, Comp Sci \& Engn Coll, Shenyang, Peoples R China.
   Zhang, Kai; Mao, Zhaoyang; Cao, Peng; Liang, Wei; Yang, Jinzhu, Northeastern Univ, Comp Sci \& Engn Coll, Shenyang, Peoples R China.
